Why would someone do such a thing?

264
00:26:25.042 --> 00:26:29.088
Was the kidnapper just a total stranger?

265
00:26:30.964 --> 00:26:31.965
Yeah.

266
00:26:36.970 --> 00:26:38.680
I'd never seen him in my life.

267
00:26:40.682 --> 00:26:41.683
Ah.

268
00:26:43.352 --> 00:26:44.937
Wow.

269
00:26:47.106 --> 00:26:49.942
I mean. that's just unbelievable.

270
00:26:50.984 --> 00:26:55.322
How can someone be so horrible?
It's like something out of a movie.

271
00:26:56.031 --> 00:26:57.074
I know.

272
00:27:00.661 --> 00:27:01.703
I wish they'd die.

273
00:27:02.246 --> 00:27:04.039
I'm so hungry.

274
00:27:06.959 --> 00:27:08.669
Those people should be killed.

275
00:27:09.253 --> 00:27:11.463
Those disgusting vermin
don't deserve to live.

276
00:27:16.093 --> 00:27:18.637
Ah. Gosh. I totally forgot.

277
00:27:19.263 --> 00:27:20.305
You can use my phone.

278
00:27:22.391 --> 00:27:25.561
- Oh. I'm so sorry.
- No. it's fine.: cue

279
00:27:52.170 --> 00:27:54.882
Seriously. I'm starving.

280
00:27:58.010 --> 00:27:59.344
Maybe kimchi stew.

281
00:28:10.105 --> 00:28:12.107
BABY ON BOARD
61K 9024

282
00:29:02.991 --> 00:29:03.992
Hi. Ms. Ko.

283
00:29:05.827 --> 00:29:08.622
How could you just take off
without saying bye?

284
00:29:09.373 --> 00:29:10.374
You hurt my feelings.

285
00:29:14.252 --> 00:29:15.253
Tell me.

286
00:29:16.588 --> 00:29:19.007
Did you seriously think
you could get away?

287
00:29:21.093 --> 00:29:22.928
You wanted to leave that badly?

288
00:30:33.999 --> 00:30:35.958
Let me show you a way out.

289
00:31:29.638 --> 00:31:31.264
Honey. stop it.

290
00:31:34.434 --> 00:31:38.772
Why did you start without me?
I didn't give you permission.

291
00:31:43.026 --> 00:31:44.944
She wanted out.

292
00:31:44.945 --> 00:31:49.156
I get it. but now's not the time.

293
00:31:49.157 --> 00:31:51.158
You can't be so impulsive about this.

294
00:31:51.159 --> 00:31:53.662
Oh my. Look at you.

295
00:32:00.752 --> 00:32:01.837
Are you okay?

296
00:32:03.213 --> 00:32:06.299
Thank goodness I came back in time.

297
00:32:07.384 --> 00:32:09.845
My husband has a short fuse.

298
00:32:10.512 --> 00:32:11.762
You all right?

299
00:32:13.515 --> 00:32:15.392
Now.

300
00:32:16.101 --> 00:32:19.271
Okay. Breathe.

301
00:32:21.606 --> 00:32:23.733
Keep doing that.

302
00:32:27.195 --> 00:32:29.114
Oh. you feeling any better?

303
00:32:29.698 --> 00:32:31.408
Who the hell are you?

304
00:32:32.659 --> 00:32:34.536
What do you mean? It's me.

305
00:32:35.287 --> 00:32:37.455
Oh. Do you not recognize me?

306
00:32:40.959 --> 00:32:42.751
Ah!

307
00:32:42.752 --> 00:32:44.170
Shh!

308
00:32:44.171 --> 00:32:47.673
Be quiet! You'll get us both in trouble!

309
00:32:49.801 --> 00:32:50.802
Oh.

310
00:32:53.847 --> 00:32:55.182
Are you okay?

311
00:32:56.933 --> 00:32:58.268
Are you hurt at all?

312
00:32:58.852 --> 00:33:01.479
You must be pretty confused.

313
00:33:02.189 --> 00:33:03.190
Who the hell are you?

314
00:33:03.815 --> 00:33:07.444
Don't make loud noises.
You'll be in trouble.

315
00:33:08.111 --> 00:33:09.779
What the hell are you saying?

316
00:33:10.405 --> 00:33:11.531
Shh!

317
00:33:12.199 --> 00:33:13.616
Be quiet!

318
00:33:13.617 --> 00:33:15.660
You'll get us both in trouble!

319
00:33:17.871 --> 00:33:19.831
Excuse me. what did you just say?

320
00:33:20.457 --> 00:33:23.667
We'll get in trouble
with the guy who locked us up here.

321
00:33:23.668 --> 00:33:25.962
Are you locked up
against your will too?

322
00:33:26.463 --> 00:33:27.464
What the…

323
00:33:28.048 --> 00:33:30.842
Damn it. I screwed up.

324
00:33:32.552 --> 00:33:34.095
Hey. Seyun.

325
00:33:34.721 --> 00:33:37.056
When you get out of here.

326
00:33:37.057 --> 00:33:40.602
can you let the police know…

327
00:33:42.312 --> 00:33:46.775
that Lee Seonja from Songmu-dong
died in this place?

328
00:33:49.527 --> 00:33:50.946
Oh. for crying out loud.

329
00:33:54.616 --> 00:33:56.159
Ms. Lee Seonja?

330
00:33:57.535 --> 00:33:59.703
Yeah. it's me.

331
00:33:59.704 --> 00:34:01.206
Remember me now?

332
00:35:04.978 --> 00:35:06.104
SERVICE LOG

333
00:35:34.007 --> 00:35:35.800
RESIDENT REGISTRATION CARD
HEO JAEIL

334
00:35:36.593 --> 00:35:37.677
"Heo Jaeil."

335
00:35:38.762 --> 00:35:40.764
RESIDENT REGISTRATION CARD
HEO JAEIL

336
00:35:49.481 --> 00:35:52.609
<i>Well. I just happened to be
in the area. so I got here fast.</i>

337
00:35:54.778 --> 00:35:56.695
All right. we're moving out.

338
00:35:56.696 --> 00:35:58.657
…and let's see
how you feel by then.

339
00:35:59.783 --> 00:36:00.784
Okay. thank you.

340
00:36:01.743 --> 00:36:02.744
No.

341
00:36:12.629 --> 00:36:14.130
Who are you people?

342
00:36:14.798 --> 00:36:16.216
Have a seat.

343
00:36:16.883 --> 00:36:19.719
What is it that you want from me?

344
00:36:20.428 --> 00:36:21.888
Why are you doing this to me?

345
00:36:23.807 --> 00:36:26.726
You're not here
because we wanted you here.

346
00:36:28.144 --> 00:36:29.895
What's that supposed to mean?

347
00:36:29.896 --> 00:36:32.773
This is what your husband wanted.

348
00:36:32.774 --> 00:36:34.858
You know this already.

349
00:36:34.859 --> 00:36:36.486
Why do you keep acting dumb?

350
00:36:37.570 --> 00:36:38.571
Honey.

351
00:36:39.572 --> 00:36:42.575
Ms. Ko. I told you already.

352
00:36:43.201 --> 00:36:45.744
Mr. Kang put me up to all of it.

353
00:36:45.745 --> 00:36:47.622
No. that's a lie.

354
00:36:48.248 --> 00:36:49.540
I don't believe you.

355
00:36:49.541 --> 00:36:53.378
You must be in denial. huh?

356
00:36:59.259 --> 00:37:00.260
Oh. my back.

357
00:37:01.136 --> 00:37:02.386
<i>But you know.</i>

358
00:37:02.387 --> 00:37:06.349
- <i>there's a limit to how much you can lie.</i>
- Here. Look.

359
00:37:06.891 --> 00:37:12.271
<i>So I said we should get divorced.</i>

360
00:37:12.272 --> 00:37:16.359
<i>But she said she didn't want to.
Well. she said she'd never do it.</i>

361
00:37:21.322 --> 00:37:24.159
But h-h-how could this be?

362
00:37:25.618 --> 00:37:26.619
Who is this guy?

363
00:37:37.297 --> 00:37:39.215
It can't be.

364
00:37:50.935 --> 00:37:55.523
Seyun…

365
00:37:56.649 --> 00:37:57.776
Seyun…

366
00:38:00.820 --> 00:38:05.158
<i>I want you to get rid of my wife.</i>

367
00:38:06.618 --> 00:38:07.952
<i>What? What did you say?</i>

368
00:38:08.828 --> 00:38:10.497
<i>Get rid of my wife.</i>

369
00:38:13.166 --> 00:38:14.501
Ms. Ko.

370
00:38:15.960 --> 00:38:17.378
How does that make you feel?

371
00:38:20.006 --> 00:38:21.633
I know this is fake.

372
00:38:25.595 --> 00:38:27.722
There's no way he said anything like that.

373
00:38:28.348 --> 00:38:30.474
I know you don't want to believe it.

374
00:38:30.475 --> 00:38:31.476
But hey.

375
00:38:32.268 --> 00:38:38.024
You already know
that your husband doesn't love you.

376
00:38:41.653 --> 00:38:43.111
<i>Let's put an end to this.</i>

377
00:38:43.112 --> 00:38:44.113
What?

378
00:38:45.031 --> 00:38:46.032
I want a divorce.

379
00:38:51.162 --> 00:38:53.330
Hey. are you crying?

380
00:38:53.331 --> 00:38:55.791
Oh. no. She's crying.

381
00:38:55.792 --> 00:38:59.045
Oh. no. Poor thing.

382
00:39:06.761 --> 00:39:08.930
Hold me.

383
00:40:11.284 --> 00:40:13.578
PRINTER AND DIGITAL COPIER
RENTAL. SALES. AND REPAIR

384
00:40:33.556 --> 00:40:35.391
Okay. thank you.

385
00:40:37.268 --> 00:40:39.562
All right. we're moving out.

386
00:40:53.409 --> 00:40:55.036
They were colleagues.

387
00:40:59.290 --> 00:41:02.502
April 17.

388
00:41:04.587 --> 00:41:06.464
April 17.

389
00:41:09.592 --> 00:41:14.305
April 17…

390
00:41:14.889 --> 00:41:16.933
"Heo. Noh."

391
00:41:18.017 --> 00:41:19.268
"Heo…"

392
00:41:20.770 --> 00:41:23.523
"Noh."

393
00:41:38.788 --> 00:41:41.374
RESIDENT REGISTRATION CARD
NOH MANHUI

394
00:41:42.834 --> 00:41:43.960
"Noh Manhui."

395
00:42:34.761 --> 00:42:36.429
Will you be my boyfriend?

396
00:42:51.819 --> 00:42:53.321
Wow.

397
00:42:55.198 --> 00:42:57.075
- Whoo! Go on. blow it out!
- Whoo! Come on! Blow it out!

398
00:42:59.202 --> 00:43:00.536
Good job!

399
00:43:01.162 --> 00:43:03.705
One. two. three!

400
00:43:03.706 --> 00:43:05.041
- Cheese!
- Cheese.

401
00:43:12.381 --> 00:43:15.468
It's 21-5 Yangsan-ro.

402
00:43:16.302 --> 00:43:18.054
It's 21-5 Yangsan-ro.

403
00:43:27.271 --> 00:43:28.356
Mmm.

404
00:43:29.107 --> 00:43:31.359
Here.

405
00:43:34.487 --> 00:43:35.821
- Hey. honey?
- Yeah?

406
00:43:35.822 --> 00:43:37.197
Is this it?

407
00:43:37.198 --> 00:43:38.533
What?

408
00:43:39.992 --> 00:43:42.160
Nothing. it's just…

409
00:43:42.161 --> 00:43:45.914
Did you want grilled ribs or something
after you blew three billion?

410
00:43:45.915 --> 00:43:47.458
We had ribs?

411
00:43:48.668 --> 00:43:50.294
You don't have to eat. you know.

412
00:43:51.504 --> 00:43:53.214
I never said I didn't want to eat.

413
00:43:56.509 --> 00:43:57.969
You know…

414
00:43:59.095 --> 00:44:04.350
I checked out the garden out back.
and the whole thing's frozen solid.

415
00:44:04.934 --> 00:44:05.935
Already?

416
00:44:07.019 --> 00:44:09.147
It probably won't thaw until March.

417
00:44:10.064 --> 00:44:12.649
Seriously? That's so far away.

418
00:44:12.650 --> 00:44:15.403
That's exactly what I'm saying.
The freezer's packed.

419
00:44:16.195 --> 00:44:18.196
What if we chop them up real small?

420
00:44:18.197 --> 00:44:19.740
I said it's packed.

421
00:44:29.375 --> 00:44:30.376
Who is it?

422
00:44:32.420 --> 00:44:35.756
And by the way.
we might want to air out the basement.

423
00:44:36.716 --> 00:44:37.717
Does it still smell?

424
00:44:38.217 --> 00:44:40.552
I said I'm sensitive to smell.

425
00:44:40.553 --> 00:44:42.470
But I've already aired it out.

426
00:44:42.471 --> 00:44:44.724
You probably didn't do it properly.

427
00:44:45.433 --> 00:44:46.434
Mmm.

428
00:44:47.101 --> 00:44:49.603
Okay. I'll pick up some bleach.

429
00:44:49.604 --> 00:44:52.147
No way. Don't use bleach.

430
00:44:52.148 --> 00:44:53.940
Geez. you don't let me do anything.

431
00:44:53.941 --> 00:44:57.153
It stinks even more when the smells mix.
I've already told you.

432
00:44:58.863 --> 00:45:01.532
Okay. fine. I'll take care of it.

433
00:45:02.033 --> 00:45:05.036
- I'll pick up some peroxide or something.
- Yeah. there you go. hmm?

434
00:45:05.870 --> 00:45:07.496
- Hurry. or you'll be late.
- Okay.

435
00:45:08.623 --> 00:45:10.332
You like these. Have some more.

436
00:45:10.333 --> 00:45:12.001
Thanks.

437
00:45:21.802 --> 00:45:24.096
<i>You will soon arrive at your destination.</i>

438
00:45:53.376 --> 00:45:56.711
JANG DOSIK
SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

439
00:45:56.712 --> 00:45:57.838
MESSAGES

440
00:47:22.006 --> 00:47:24.383
Oh my God.

441
00:47:25.468 --> 00:47:26.635
Is Noh Manhui home?

442
00:47:28.262 --> 00:47:30.097
Wait. wha-what are you talking about?

443
00:47:36.479 --> 00:47:38.689
I'm asking. Is your husband home?

444
00:47:39.565 --> 00:47:42.567
No. H-He's not home right now.

445
00:47:42.568 --> 00:47:43.819
And my wife?

446
00:47:46.655 --> 00:47:47.740
Where's my wife?

447
00:47:49.075 --> 00:47:51.160
- Who are you talking abou...
- My wife. Ko Seyun!

448
00:47:52.995 --> 00:47:54.913
Where are you keeping her?

449
00:47:54.914 --> 00:47:57.458
I don't know. I don't know anything.

450
00:47:58.209 --> 00:48:01.044
Wait! I really have no idea!

451
00:48:01.045 --> 00:48:03.588
I don't know anything about that. Please!

452
00:48:09.261 --> 00:48:10.930
INCOMING CALL
MY BABY

453
00:48:11.555 --> 00:48:13.014
Hey. honey.

454
00:48:13.015 --> 00:48:14.350
<i>Sweetie.</i>

455
00:48:15.518 --> 00:48:17.186
Hey. what's wrong?

456
00:48:18.771 --> 00:48:19.980
<i>Mr. Noh.</i>

457
00:48:21.232 --> 00:48:23.317
<i>It's me. Kang Taeju.</i>

458
00:48:28.989 --> 00:48:30.032
Mr. Kang?

459
00:48:32.159 --> 00:48:34.328
Noh Manhui. I finally got your name.

460
00:48:34.995 --> 00:48:36.539
<i>What are you doing there?</i>

461
00:48:37.373 --> 00:48:41.419
Sweetie. he's got a re-real gu-gun on him.

462
00:48:43.546 --> 00:48:45.005
Wait. I…

463
00:48:45.589 --> 00:48:48.341
Look. Just hold on a moment.
I'm making my way there now.

464
00:48:48.342 --> 00:48:49.385
<i>If we could just talk…</i>

465
00:48:50.261 --> 00:48:51.970
<i>Honey! No!</i>

466
00:48:51.971 --> 00:48:55.306
Oh. no! No!

467
00:48:55.307 --> 00:48:57.268
Honey. are you shot?

468
00:49:02.982 --> 00:49:04.483
Next time. she will be.

469
00:49:07.403 --> 00:49:08.696
<i>Noh Manhui!</i>

470
00:49:10.239 --> 00:49:15.619
This man is literally holding a
gun to my head right now.: cue

471
00:49:16.328 --> 00:49:17.621
You hear me?

472
00:49:21.959 --> 00:49:27.214
Mr. Kang! Please. Mr. Kang!
Please don't do this!

473
00:49:29.049 --> 00:49:30.092
Talk.

474
00:49:31.635 --> 00:49:33.387
Where is my wife?

475
00:51:25.833 --> 00:51:28.127
- Honey.
- Honey.

476
00:51:37.219 --> 00:51:38.554
Seyun. are you okay?

477
00:51:39.722 --> 00:51:41.140
Are you hurt anywhere?

478
00:51:43.892 --> 00:51:45.352
It's all over now. Let's go home.

479
00:51:47.354 --> 00:51:49.023
We have to get out of here.

480
00:51:49.523 --> 00:51:50.816
You think you can walk?

481
00:51:52.359 --> 00:51:53.360
Don't touch me.

482
00:51:54.987 --> 00:51:56.447
Keep your hands off me.

483
00:51:57.948 --> 00:51:58.949
What's wrong?

484
00:52:00.534 --> 00:52:02.661
How could you do this to me?

485
00:52:04.788 --> 00:52:06.497
What do you mean?

486
00:52:06.498 --> 00:52:08.042
I saw the video.

487
00:52:12.379 --> 00:52:14.673
Where you tell that guy to kill me.

488
00:52:18.052 --> 00:52:20.929
Oh. that?

489
00:52:22.181 --> 00:52:23.641
That's a huge misunderstanding.

490
00:52:24.767 --> 00:52:26.934
I can explain everything.

491
00:52:26.935 --> 00:52:30.855
but right now. we have to get out of here.
We'll talk once we're out. okay? I'll…

492
00:52:30.856 --> 00:52:31.857
No!

493
00:52:36.320 --> 00:52:38.280
We don't have time for this right now!

494
00:52:39.156 --> 00:52:40.574
Please.

495
00:52:41.450 --> 00:52:43.494
We have to get the hell out of here!

496
00:52:49.750 --> 00:52:50.751
Seyun.

497
00:52:52.169 --> 00:52:54.505
Seyun. you have to believe me.

498
00:52:55.172 --> 00:52:58.591
That video. It's all a misunderstanding.

499
00:52:58.592 --> 00:52:59.968
I can explain all of it.

500
00:53:00.761 --> 00:53:01.804
Seyun.

501
00:53:02.805 --> 00:53:04.139
I'm telling you the truth.

502
00:53:04.640 --> 00:53:05.890
Please.

503
00:53:05.891 --> 00:53:07.393
Please just believe me.

504
00:54:39.359 --> 00:54:40.360
Honey!

505
00:54:41.612 --> 00:54:44.947
Mr. Kang. What are you doing here?

506
00:54:44.948 --> 00:54:45.991
No!

507
00:54:47.409 --> 00:54:48.826
Goddamn it!

508
00:55:40.504 --> 00:55:42.589
- Taeju!
- Oh. honey!

509
00:55:43.465 --> 00:55:46.008
Honey!

510
00:55:46.009 --> 00:55:49.971
Are you okay? Look at me. You okay?

511
00:55:54.226 --> 00:55:56.894
Honey. look at me.

512
00:55:56.895 --> 00:55:58.771
Go after them already.

513
00:55:58.772 --> 00:56:00.523
I said. are you okay?

514
00:56:00.524 --> 00:56:01.983
Noh Manhui!

515
00:56:01.984 --> 00:56:03.944
Chase them down and kill them!

516
00:56:50.824 --> 00:56:51.867
Are you okay?

517
00:56:52.784 --> 00:56:53.869
Yeah.

518
00:56:55.203 --> 00:56:56.913
We're going to get out of here.

519
00:56:57.539 --> 00:57:00.542
And I'll clear up this misunderstanding.

520
00:57:02.044 --> 00:57:03.253
You just need to trust me.

521
00:57:55.764 --> 00:57:57.306
Se-Se-Seyun.

522
00:57:57.307 --> 00:57:59.518
Seyun? Seyun.

523
00:58:00.352 --> 00:58:01.353
Seyun!

524
00:58:07.484 --> 00:58:08.860
Seyun!

525
00:58:30.549 --> 00:58:32.550
Seyun.

526
00:58:32.551 --> 00:58:33.968
Seyun. come on.

527
00:58:33.969 --> 00:58:36.595
Seyun. Come on. Please.

528
00:58:36.596 --> 00:58:37.930
Seyun.

529
00:58:37.931 --> 00:58:39.725
Seyun. can you hear me?

530
00:58:40.892 --> 00:58:42.476
Hey. are you okay?

531
00:58:42.477 --> 00:58:45.187
Let's go. Come on. Seyun.

532
00:58:45.188 --> 00:58:46.189
Honey.

533
00:58:47.065 --> 00:58:48.066
Honey.

534
00:58:48.692 --> 00:58:50.861
Look out!

535
00:58:53.155 --> 00:58:58.075
THE HUSBAND

536
00:59:38.617 --> 00:59:40.242
{\an8}- Seyun!
- Don't move!

537
00:59:40.243 --> 00:59:41.327
{\an8}<i>Stop right there!</i>

538
00:59:41.328 --> 00:59:42.661
{\an8}<i>We've lost the suspect.</i>

539
00:59:42.662 --> 00:59:45.164
{\an8}<i>Also. we've located a female
inside the suspect's residence…</i>

540
00:59:45.165 --> 00:59:47.166
{\an8}<i>Her legs will be
permanently paralyzed</i>

541
00:59:47.167 --> 00:59:48.584
{\an8}<i>if she doesn't get surgery right now.</i>

542
00:59:48.585 --> 00:59:49.961
{\an8}<i>She may even die.</i>

543
00:59:50.962 --> 00:59:54.423
{\an8}<i>So you're asking to have her
operated on at our hospital?</i>

544
00:59:54.424 --> 00:59:55.508
{\an8}That criminal?

545
00:59:55.509 --> 00:59:56.801
{\an8}<i>What's this guy's deal?</i>

546
00:59:56.802 --> 00:59:59.970
{\an8}<i>You messed with the wrong person.</i>

547
00:59:59.971 --> 01:00:02.139
{\an8}I will not let that surgery happen. Never!

548
01:00:02.140 --> 01:00:03.390
{\an8}<i>I'm doing this surgery.</i>

549
01:00:03.391 --> 01:00:06.268
{\an8}<i>I want the truth.
I want to know why they kidnapped me.</i>

550
01:00:06.269 --> 01:00:08.229
{\an8}<i>I'll operate on you.</i>

551
01:00:08.230 --> 01:00:09.815
{\an8}Don't worry. I'm a doctor.

552
01:00:10.315 --> 01:00:12.317
{\an8}Translated by Hyun Sik Yoon

552
